      <h2>This is a working sanctuary.</h2>
      <p>A few things to set expectations:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>We're 68 miles south of Austin, 42 miles east of San Antonio. You'll need a car.</li>
        <li>Early mornings are noisy in the best way: roosters, donkeys, cows, and dogs are all up with the sun.</li>
        <li>The property is rural. Expect uneven ground, dust, mud depending on weather, and active farm equipment.</li>
        <li>We cannot accommodate guest pets on the property due to biosecurity.</li>
        <li>No smoking anywhere on the property.</li>
        <li>All proceeds from stays go directly to the care of our animals.</li>
      </ul>

